{"tid":441322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【住中半山千萬豪宅都揸黑的】富貴司機上山頂貪30蚊衰咗","createTime":"2017-10-19T14:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T04:00:25.000Z","uid":84436,"like":95,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"073a489fa813403e3dfee49ec104c23e5f5f4198","tid":441322,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171019/57353320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171019%2F57353320&d=LwSsvyZ8f9r1mutVEsvrM4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=bdb456b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171019%2F57353320&h=db8f5f70\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171019/57353320</a><br />\n<br />\n警方山頂分區人員於今日傍晚約6時，在中區打擊的士濫收車資罪行，其間派員喬裝乘客，乘搭一輛的士由中區花園道纜車站前往山頂道118號。的士司機收取車資100元，僅較正常約70元車資多收30元，人員抵步付款後隨即表露身份，拘捕61歲姓任男司機。<br />\n<br />\n涉案司機涉嫌濫收車資，及沒有撥動的士計程錶指示器，正被扣留調查。消息稱，涉案之的士司機同時亦為車主，家住港島中半山堅尼地道慧景臺一個巿值千多萬元的單位。現場消息稱，警員對於他僅為多收30元以身試法，不免摸不着頭腦。"},{"pid":"4e8d93799e585e6405e13ff923038d64cab523d8","tid":441322,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddf8083131daf809df11aed236c57556ff77d56","tid":441322,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f447e4ea6f8d800ebd96852a837b78f33583b7b5","tid":441322,"uid":48964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:19:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自住冇關係架</blockquote><br />\n分分鐘按左仲供緊"},{"pid":"62a0e48471addbd0146f0c42ec5694cc311b6dc4","tid":441322,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d43d509b9285d